Program: Outlook
Title: My wife is on hunger strike
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010pd66
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 27 Nov 2012
As imprisoned Iranian lawyer Nasrin Sotoudeh ends her sixth week on hunger strike, her husband Reza Khandan talks about his fears for her and his family. Also Kwasi Afari Minta, the music producer from Ghana who was caught up in the worst ever fire on London's Underground. Picture: Nasrin Sotoudeh Show less